broadside broadcast by official radio kabul 
these groundless allegations which are being made in order to 
mislead public opinion are far from the truth and are counted as 
another design for creating obstacles in the way of the return of 
the refugees the radio quoted him as saying 
he said the measures taken were political social and 
economic but he gave no details 
