if the syrians attempt to enter by force 
that would sharpen the strain on an alliance between syria and 
iran which has been imperiled by hezbollahs efforts to dominate 
the 12 million shiites in lebanon 
the syrians have 25000 troops based in northern and eastern 
lebanon under a 1976 peacekeeping mandate from the arab league 
they also deployed 7500 troops in west beirut in february 1987 
to curb three years of militia violence 
