drug cartel and manuel noriega said damato 
nunn said he believes that you dont indict a leader of a 
foreign country unless you know how youre going to follow through 
on it apparently we did not have ways to go about it plans for 
extradition 
certainly weve dug ourselves into a hole now said nunn 
dropping the charges is sending a very bad signal 
