sometimes referred to as the rich countries club the oecd 
groups the 24 main industrialized nations and focuses on economic 
issues for the group of seven main democracies the oecd meeting 
will serve as a dress rehearsal for nexts month world economic 
summit in ottawa 
on trade the officials said the current round of uruguay 
